Hello I am from team 5012 and our robot is not reading the joystick inputs for our code. We are using the Tuner X Swerve builder API and I have followed all the basic instructions for setting up the API. I’ve tried changing the variable for the controller where its Xboxcontroller, Joystick, and even CommandXboxController in which the robot still didn’t move even when I was moving the joysticks around. As well as moving the set control command in different places. Any help would be appreciated, thank you.

Note: I forgot to change the DriveRequestType.Velocity back to DriveRequestType.OpenLoopVoltage in the Robot file

Swerve instructions: Swerve Builder API
